title: The Enforcer
description: When Juliana Redding, a beautiful young aspiring actress, is found beaten and strangled in her Santa Monica bungalow, the case turns into a real-life Hollywood thriller. Could it be the boyfriend with a bad temper, the married surgeon - or a female assassin?
author: content@audiochuck.com (audiochuck)
